import M1 from "./svg-8.svg";
import M2 from "./branch.svg";
import M3 from "./contact.svg";

export const homeObjOne = {
  id: "about",
  lightBg: false,
  lightText: true,
  lightTextDesc: true,
  topLine: "XFACE",
  headline: "WHO WE ARE ?",
  description:
    "We are here with intentation to change the world by digitaly,And we will give you the 100% of us.You can also send us your work details to get a job in XFACE.",
  buttonLable: "Send Details",
  imgStart: false,
  alt: "Web",
  img: M1,
  dark: true,
  primary: true,
  darkText: false,
};

export const homeObjTow = {
  id: "Discover",
  lightBg: true,
  lightText: false,
  lightTextDesc: false,
  topLine: "OTHER BRANCH",
  headline: "We have different branch for evey filed",
  description:
    "We are working in fields like software develpomnet , penetration testing and many more. ",
  buttonLable: "Learn more",
  imgStart: true,
  img: M2,
  alt: "Fields",
  dark: false,
  primary: false,
  darkText: true,
};

export const homeObjThree = {
  id: "Contact US",
  lightBg: true,
  lightText: false,
  lightTextDesc: false,
  topLine: "Feedback",
  headline: "Send your valuable feekback to us ☺",
  description:
    "Please send feedback related to our work or any suggestion related to our work. we are happy to check your valuable feedback.",
  buttonLable: "Feedback",
  imgStart: true,
  img: M3,
  alt: "Contact",
  dark: false,
  primary: false,
  darkText: true,
};
